{"content":"<p><img src=\"/body/yellow_5.webp\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<div class=\"hint-container tip\">\n<p class=\"hint-container-title\">语句</p>\n<p>是一段可以执行的代码,重点是用来执行的,不是用来计算某个具体结果</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hint-container tip\">\n<p class=\"hint-container-title\">表达式</p>\n<p>在程序中能够得出一个计算出一个具体的结果，比如<code v-pre>x = 3</code>、<code v-pre>3*4</code>、<code v-pre>i++</code></p>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"分支语句\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#分支语句\"><span>分支语句</span></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"单条件判断\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#单条件判断\"><span>单条件判断</span></a></h3>\n<div class=\"hint-container tip\">\n<p class=\"hint-container-title\">提示</p>\n<p>程序在执行的时候,如果条件成立就执行某一行代码, 如果条件不成立则执行其他代码</p>\n</div>\n<h4 id=\"if单分支\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#if单分支\"><span>if单分支</span></a></h4>\n<div class=\"hint-container tip\">\n<p class=\"hint-container-title\">提示</p>\n<p>else语句可不写</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"language-txt line-numbers-mode\" data-ext=\"txt\" data-title=\"txt\"><button class=\"copy\" title=\"复制代码\" data-copied=\"已复制\"></button><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\"\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span>if(条件){</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>else{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>    执行的代码</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>}</span></span></code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"line-numbers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div><p>如果条件为真，就执行if里语句，否则执行else语句</p>\n<p><strong>账户登录演示</strong></p>\n<div class=\"language-js line-numbers-mode\" data-ext=\"js\" data-title=\"js\"><button class=\"copy\" title=\"复制代码\" data-copied=\"已复制\"></button><pre class=\"shiki shiki-t